products.description: Is it a dream or reality? This radiant moon highlights the landscape as the still water reflects the endless sky above.

Get these two paintings as a bundle pack. Red Sun depicts the blazing sun before it sets just above the treeline. Lakeside Coffee expresses the calmness of sipping warm coffee lakeside on a cloudy morning in the forested mountains.
These three gnomes are here to protect you from the darkness. They are guardians that keep the nightmares away.
What is better than some lavender with tea and candles?
